  <brief_title>HECTHOR: Humira to Spare Steroids in Giant Cell Arteritis</brief_title>
  <official_title>HECTHOR: A Pilot Multicenter Double-blind Randomised Study of 3 Months Treatment With Humira Added to Steroids in Giant Cell Arteritis</official_title>
